snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights createConversation Sample
snippets.description: Creates a conversation. Note that this method does not support audio transcription or redaction. Use `conversations.upload` instead.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights uploadConversation Sample
snippets.description: Create a long-running conversation upload operation. This method differs from `CreateConversation` by allowing audio transcription and optional DLP redaction.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights createAnalysis Sample
snippets.description: Creates an analysis. The long running operation is done when the analysis has completed.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights bulkAnalyzeConversations Sample
snippets.description: Analyzes multiple conversations in a single request.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights bulkDeleteConversations Sample
snippets.description: Deletes multiple conversations in a single request.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights ingestConversations Sample
snippets.description: Imports conversations and processes them according to the user's configuration.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights exportInsightsData Sample
snippets.description: Export insights data to a destination defined in the request body.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights deployIssueModel Sample
snippets.description: Deploys an issue model. Returns an error if a model is already deployed. An issue model can only be used in analysis after it has been deployed.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights undeployIssueModel Sample
snippets.description: Undeploys an issue model. An issue model can not be used in analysis after it has been undeployed.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights exportIssueModel Sample
snippets.description: Exports an issue model to the provided destination.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights importIssueModel Sample
snippets.description: Imports an issue model from a Cloud Storage bucket.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights initializeEncryptionSpec Sample
snippets.description: Initializes a location-level encryption key specification. An error will result if the location has resources already created before the initialization. After the encryption specification is initialized at a location, it is immutable and all newly created resources under the location will be encrypted with the existing specification.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights tuneQaScorecardRevision Sample
snippets.description: Fine tune one or more QaModels.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights listQaScorecardRevisions Sample
snippets.description: Lists all revisions under the parent QaScorecard.

snippets.title: ContactCenterInsights listAllFeedbackLabels Sample
snippets.description: List all feedback labels by project number.
